They come close -> start recording
	if they walk away -> stop & save and notify
	if they've been there 90s stop save and notify
	if they push the button, discard recording and send snapshot and notify
If the button is pushed, send snapshot and notify

Live Feed:
	Only retains the last few frames, rest is deleted
	Speed at which it updates is based on the state of the application logic
		Normal framerate  - 0.2
		Any signal - 3-5~	
